knowledgeGraph.title: UC Davis Medical Center
knowledgeGraph.description: UC Davis Medical Center is part of UC Davis Health and a major academic health center located in Sacramento, California. It is owned and operated by the University of California as part of its University of California, Davis campus.

organic.title: UC Davis Health | University of California, Davis
organic.snippet: We're committed to better health for all through our unique combination of personalized care and expertise as a leading academic health system.

organic.title: MyUCDavisHealth | UC Davis Health
organic.snippet: UC Davis Health patients can use MyUCDavisHealth to communicate with their care team, review their medical record, and much more — from any device.

organic.title: Services and Specialties | UC Davis Health
organic.snippet: UC Davis Health provides leading-edge radiology and imaging services, such as X-Rays and fluoroscopy, CT scans, MRIs, PET and EXPLORER total body scans.
